Create Both  # Automatically create missing mailboxes
Expunge Both
MaxMessages 1000


IMAPAccount gg
Host imap.gmail.com
User egeavunc@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass mail/google"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gg-remote
Account gg

MaildirStore gg-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/gg/  # The trailing "/" is important
Inbox ~/mail/gg/Inbox

Channel gg
Master :gg-remote:
Slave :gg-local:
Patterns INBOX "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Drafts"
ExpireUnread yes
SyncState *  # Save the synchronization state files in the relevant directory



